    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pottery decorated primarily with slip that is black in color. Examples are from 12th-3rd century BCE Nepal, 3d-2nd century Praeneste, ancient Gaul, and other places.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
